            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>CORPORATE INFO</h3>
                <ul class="footer-links">
                    <li><a href="/career">Career at Blur Vintage ★</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About Blur Vintage ★</a></li>
