            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>SIGN UP FOR UPDATES</h3>
                <p>Sign up now and be the first to know exclusive offers, latest fashion news and style tips!</p>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i></a>
